                       IIInnntttrrrooo tttooo IIIIII:iii


CCChhhaaarrraaacccttteeerrrsss dddeeefffiiinnneeeddd fffooorrr ttthhhiiisss sssccceeennneee:

    1. <pro>   Professor . . . . . . . . . .  (Professor)

111-PPPRRROOOFFFEEESSSSSSOOORRR:   Now,  if  we're all QUITE ready? As well as a
   place for learning, the university is a place  to  relax,
   to  be  entertained  and  to  mature into fine upstanding
   human beings. Because of this, at  least  one  university
   set up a faculty of Human Kinetics and Leisure Studies to
   examine students at rest and students in  motion,  or  to
   put  it  more  succinctly, students in bed. In the 1800's
   they had the moves and didn't need the rest, as we  shall
   soon see.

                          - fin -






































